# Dependencies
# No trailing slash: ignore a `node_modules` DIRECTORY *and* a stray
# `node_modules` symlink. A dir-only `node_modules/` rule let a self-referential
# `node_modules -> node_modules` symlink slip past gitignore and get committed
# (#3041), re-materialising an infinite symlink loop on every checkout/reset that
# broke every npm build with `spawn ELOOP`. See
# docs/bug-autopsies/node-modules-eloop-symlink.md.
node_modules

